Issue: Youtube HTML5 player only allows 360p quality
Date: 1st September 2015

Solution
--------

Resources: http://www.linuxveda.com/2015/06/29/get-1080p-youtubes-html5-player-firefox-linux/

Enter "about:config" in the url bar and enable the following extensions,
- media.mediasource.enabled - True
- media.mediasource.webm.enabled - False (enabling this causing playback issues and high cpu usage)

Install gst-libav package.

